title: Pickup Bed Extender by Dee Zee
description:
Whether you're loading up your truck bed with supplies for the jobsite or packing it up for a weekend getaway, Dee Zee's Pickup Truck Bed Extender allows you to maximize your hauling capacity with an extra 20 inches!
